ort us by recognizing the value of foresight. We couldn=E2=80=99t do our w=
ork without them. As we close the year=2C we ask our community to consider=
 making a year-end donation that will help us scale our ability to bring t=
he gift of foresight to more diverse communities worldwide and to contribu=
